ygData.subject: Re: New Lullaby Results
ygData.msgSnippet: Klug - I think only 3 attempts is not enough data to form a statistical sample - you may want to try this on several more occasions before deciding that a rate
ygData.messageBody:
Klug - I think only 3 attempts is not enough data to form a statistical
sample - you may want to try this on several more occasions before deciding
that a rate of 75 pct resistance.

Also - I think that the "context" of the song may come into play. Perhaps
you find an even higher resistance rate when used for "nap time" as opposed
to "sleep time"...

Slyde
